# Git remote for this repo

- **Push and pull only to:** `origin` → `https://github.com/klaronda/mintcheck.git` (repo name: **mintcheck**).
- **Do not** push website or app changes to **mintcheck-app** or any other GitHub repo unless the user explicitly asks for that repo.
- The git root for this project is the **mintcheck** repository root (the directory that contains `.git`). If the workspace is a parent path, run git commands from that root.
